{"tid":412085,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門寶田商場百佳 癲佬踢狗虐畜","createTime":"2017-09-24T10:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T13:02:37.000Z","uid":55118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8103f9f20baa29c4335513f2a50570e5bf75b1","tid":412085,"uid":55118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"((虐畜者出沒請注意))<br />\n請大家分享出去 地點係屯門寶田商場<br />\n<br />\n事緣 有個男人放低左隻狗 百佳嘅職員睇住佢唔俾佢周圍走！(強調講番聲:職員唔係幫狗主睇狗！而係隻狗仔走失左，職員幫手唔俾佢搔擾到人！)<br />\n<br />\n與百佳嘅職員完全無關 ！<br />\n<br />\n但係呢個痴線佬(剛係百佳買完嘢) 就大大聲係到嘈百佳嘅職員:呢到點可以有隻狗架！掉隻狗出去啦！<br />\n<br />\n個職員就話:我只可以喺度睇住隻狗唔可以比佢周圍走！然後等佢主人返嚟！<br />\n<br />\n然後個男人就發晒癲話:屌！等我來！((即刻放低手上嘅嘢沖咗入百佳))<br />\n<br />\n片段見到佢掉狗踢狗！！極之冇人性嘅行為！<br />\n<br />\n根本係虐畜，個男人時候匆匆離去，狗狗嘅主人又不在，無奈地我不能捉住佢然後報警！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家認住呢個變態佬(生人勿近)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shopchuckle/posts/1719706201375961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshopchuckle%2Fposts%2F1719706201375961&d=SmmKGvdAKZkurWpwob5GVwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=c6a685c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shopchuckle/posts/1719706201375961</a>"},{"pid":"15d4518b7cabbaef16c44c6e94a11f3c06806510","tid":412085,"uid":88962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:39:50.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲快d刮佢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab52be0a29ee90b450cb4e62e41855f3eb6900a2","tid":412085,"uid":3063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"寶田有邊個唔癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8fa0940ae9dec6bda1f5453bcd29af0b7e7754","tid":412085,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6241d652554eb1733b8f62d30c041565b02585a3","tid":412085,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寶田有邊個唔癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm